Class PatientAppointment

java.lang.Object
sc2002.models.PatientAppointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Appointment
public class PatientAppointment extends Object implements Appointment
Manages appointments for a patient, including scheduling, rescheduling, cancelling, and viewing available slots and past outcomes.
